#

Cold Summer Borshch (Holodnyk)

15 min
$8
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

Chilled SoupSummer DishQuick Meal

Description

A refreshing, chilled beet soup perfect for hot summer days, loaded with vibrant vegetables and a hint of tanginess from sour cream.

Ingredients

  • beets: 2 medium, cooked and grated
  • cucumber: 1, diced
  • radishes: 5, sliced thin
  • green onions: 3, chopped
  • fresh dill: 2 tbsp, chopped
  • sour cream: 1 cup
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups, chilled
  • lemon juice: 2 tbsp
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
